com.quinsoft.zeidon.standardoe

Class IteratorBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.quinsoft.zeidon.standardoe.IteratorBuilder

  • public class IteratorBuilder
extends Object
    This object builds entity iterators with different options. Expected use case is: iterator = new IteratorBuilder() .setCursor( cursor ) .forTwinsOf( getEntityInstance() ) .forEntityDef( getEntityDef() ) .build();

    DG
